                     <p> 
                        <persName>
                           <forename>Ralph</forename>, the abbot</persName>, and <orgName key="org_103001">convent of Kirkestal</orgName> grant to 
                  <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename>, son of <persName>
                              <forename>Ernis</forename> of
                     <surname>Alreton</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, eleven and a half acres of land in 
                  <placeName key="place_103050">West Alreton</placeName>, which they had by the gift of 
                  <persName>his mother <forename>Juliana</forename>
                        </persName>,  at an annual rent of 6d. for all services; 
                  also they grant one other acre in <placeName key="place_103050">West Alreton</placeName> which
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Ernis</forename> his father</persName> held of them. 
                  (<origDate notBefore="1182" notAfter="1190" precision="low">c. 1182-1190</origDate>.) 
                  . </p>
